description:
Filter Params

- role (can be a single string or comma seperated strings)
- group (string)
- industry (can be a single string or comma seperated strings)

- location (can be a single string or comma seperated strings)
- education (can be a single string or comma seperated strings)

- keywords_percentage (comma seperated int values. e.g keywords_percentage=20,75)
